{{Quote|Great for planting down drainage systems and air-conditioning ducts.|[[Atin Skirata]]|<ref name="Republic Commando: Hard Contact">''[[Republic Commando: Hard Contact]]''</ref>}}
An '''improvised explosive device''', or '''IED''', was, as its name suggested, an explosive fashioned from more everyday materials not purposely designed as ordnance, including but not limited to small packs of mining explosive or "explosive barrels." These were used by [[Omega Squad]] on its mission to [[Qiilura/Legends|Qiilura]], and many were encountered by [[Delta Squad/Legends|Delta Squad]] during their [[Mission to the Chaykin Cluster|mission to the ''Prosecutor'']].

